Eighteen people are killed and at least 40 injured after a gravel truck smashes into a bus near Podolsk, Russia. (Rappler)A shallow 5.1 magnitude earthquake near Quito's capital region kills four with another three missing in a landslide. (AAP via News Limited)Typhoon Neoguri hits the main Japanese island of Honshu causing flooding, landslides and three deaths. (BBC)